FBIS3-54667 "drsov001_u_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Latvia Police Given `Temporary Rights' To Search WS3112122293 Tallinn BNS in English 1808 GMT 30 Dec 93 WS3112122293 Tallinn BNS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Riga, Dec 30, BNS -- The Latvian Cabinet granted the state police and the Home Guard temporary rights to search transportation vehicles, their drivers and passengers on the basis of grounded suspicion, beginning Dec. 31. The government motivated the decision with the increasing abuse of firearms and explosives in the republic and the fact that criminals often use cars as means of transportation. [passage omitted]
